OL,3,COfcom considering 'statutory sanction'
OL,4,Cagainst GB News over Sunak programme
OL,6,FBroadcasting regulator is considering
OL,7,F"statutory sanction" against GB News
OL,8,Fafter concluding an hour-long
OL,9,Fprogramme with Prime Minister Rishi
OL,10,FSunak broke impartiality rules.
OL,12,FThe watchdog was investigating a
OL,13,F"People's Forum" episode - which
OL,14,Ffeatured Mr Sunak in a question-and-
OL,15,Fanswer session with a studio audience
OL,16,Fabout the government's policies and
OL,17,Fperformance - after it received 547
OL,18,Fcomplaints earlier this year.
