OL,3,COfcom considering 'statutory sanction'
OL,4,Cagainst GB News over Sunak programme
OL,6,FWhile Ofcom acknowledged the contents
OL,7,Fof the programme would focus "mainly
OL,8,Fon the Conservatives Party," it found
OL,9,Ffault with the lack of challenge and
OL,10,Falternatives views presented by GB
OL,11,FNews throughout.
OL,13,FGB News has accused Ofcom of trying to
OL,14,F"silence" the channel by not allowing
OL,15,Fthe "public to question politicians
OL,16,Fdirectly" following the decision.
